title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table containing a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Open the report attached.  2. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.  3. Preview the report.  4. Attempt to export the data from the table.  Note the exception thrown.
